data.description: This is a must see stunning oversized 2-bedroom, 2 bath single-family home, with NO HOA sitting on almost a HALF ACRE lot.  Home backs up to a canal and features a beautiful gazebo and large open backyard space!! Updates include, newer roof, brand new kitchen & SS appliances, bathroom with vessel sinks, and a custom-made bamboo bathtub. Oversized 2 car garage has A/C and plenty of space for storage. Home is conveniently located East of US 1, close to shopping and the beach. Non-working fireplace.
